data.description: Welcome to the wonderful waterfront boating community of Gulf Harbors, woodlands! This waterfront home is move-in ready and with your boat in your backyard, and on your 10,000lb lift, you are minutes from the Gulf of Mexico. This is a cozy 2 bed 2 bath home, attached 2 car garage with an inside laundry room, fenced yard for the dogs, and updated kitchen and baths. The home is conveniently located minutes from shopping and dining. AC was replaced in 2019, Roof in 2013, and Seawall in 2011.
